Package: cosmic-ext-applet-systemstats
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: System monitoring applet for COSMIC desktop
 A lightweight system monitoring applet for the COSMIC desktop environment
 that displays CPU usage, memory, network speeds, and CPU/GPU temperatures
 in the system tray.
 .
 Features:
  - CPU usage percentage monitoring
  - Memory usage in GB
  - Network upload/download speeds
  - CPU and GPU temperature monitoring
  - Configurable refresh interval
  - Toggle individual monitors via TOML configuration
